OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780589464
OL,3,CHealthy Ageing: What Should You Eat?
OL,5,FThe UK has a growing elderly
OL,6,Fpopulation, with people living longer
OL,7,Fthan ever. Over the last 25 years, the
OL,8,Fnumber of people living to 100 has
OL,9,Fdoubled in the UK to over 16,000. But
OL,10,Fin the last decade, our healthy life
OL,11,Fexpectancy - the number of years that
OL,12,Fwe live in good health - has fallen
OL,13,Ffor both men and women to the age of
OL,14,F61. In this week's episode of Tonight,
OL,15,FKate Quilton has been finding out
OL,16,Fwhether building better nutritional
OL,17,Fhabits help improve and even extend
OL,18,Four life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
