PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780589464
OL,3,CHealthy Ageing: What Should You Eat?
OL,5,FTonight meets some of the eldest
OL,6,Fresidents, including three
OL,7,Fcentenarians, living in a care home in
OL,8,FCheshire. They share what they believe
OL,9,Fhas contributed to their longevity,
OL,10,Fbelieving eating well is key.
OL,12,F"We didn't have fast food, it's a
OL,13,Fmodern thing. I'd never heard of a
OL,14,Fburger." - Iris, aged 97
OL,16,FDr David Cox, neuroscientist and
OL,17,Fauthor of The Age Code says it is
OL,18,Fnever too late to make a change when
OL,19,Fit comes to our diet.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
