SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780589464
OL,3,CHealthy Ageing: What Should You Eat?
OL,5,FAround 30% of older people who are
OL,6,Fadmitted to hospital in the UK are at
OL,7,Frisk of malnourishment. Dr Sorrel
OL,8,FBurden, a dietitian and member of the
OL,9,FHealthy Ageing Research Group at The
OL,10,FUniversity of Manchester, says
OL,11,Fmalnutrition is linked to increased
OL,12,Fmortality and having a poorer immune
OL,13,Ffunction. She adds that people who are
OL,14,Fmalnourished have more contact with
OL,15,Fhealth services both in primary and
OL,16,Fsecondary care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
