SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780589464
OL,3,CHealthy Ageing: What Should You Eat?
OL,5,FiCare's Meals on Wheels service in
OL,6,FWigan delivers around 250 meals a day.
OL,7,FServices like this can be a lifeline
OL,8,Ffor the elderly, providing both daily
OL,9,Fnutrition and social interaction.
OL,11,F"Just having a 5 minute chat with
OL,12,Fthese people and making sure they're
OL,13,Fhaving something to eat, it makes a
OL,14,Fgreat difference to them. People think
OL,15,Fwe're just a meal delivery service,
OL,16,Fbut we're not, we're so much more." -
OL,17,FGemma, community assistant at iCare
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
